        <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
        <p>
            <b>Q.</b> Do I need to make an account to get Plus?
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>A.</b> You do not need to create an account of any kind. You just need an email address. 
        </p>
        <hr>
        <p>
            <b>Q.</b> I purchased Plus, but it is no longer activated.
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>A.</b> Go into your email, find the receipt from Ko-fi,
            and click on the button to re-activate Plus.
        </p>

